          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>National Park Service Transparency and Accountability Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the National Park Service (NPS) to submit to Congress a report that contains: (1) an evaluation of its capital investment strategy, (2) a determination of whether the strategy is achieving its intended outcomes, and (3) any changes to the strategy that the NPS recommends to improve such outcomes. </p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2017-03-16T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
